    "However, the presence of multiple cell types in each spot in ST data makes it difficult for these models to disentangle cell type-specific features.",
    "To overcome this limitation, Starfysh introduces a generative model with a special variational family that is structured to model the presence of multiple cell states per spot in ST data.",
    "The Starfysh generative model leverages gene set signatures (either existing signatures or signatures computed with archetypal analysis) as an empirical prior to help disentangle cell types 72.",
    "We first detail the generative model of Starfysh and then introduce its structured variational family.",
    "x i ∈ ℝ G (with G the number of observed genes) for each spot i with a generative model."
